      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELITE CHEVY (8) boasts a strong record this journey with 11 wins and five minors from 22 tries. Scored by 2 lengths last time (17.64) in a Mix 1/2/3 over 324m at this track. Looks well placed and should feature. EXPRESS ETHICS (7) was a winner (17.62) at this track two back but out of the placings last time when 8th at Bulli. Has a good record here at this journey. Should play a prominent role. SEND IT SILVER (2) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last start finished 2nd over 324m at this track beaten 0.8 lengths (17.90) behind MR. IRRELEVENT in a Mix 2/3 on February 12. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Overdue and gets his chance. PINCH POINT (1) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
